videos.headline: Ohio State with opening-drive TD
videos.description: Mike Weber runs the ball up the middle for a quick Buckeyes 4-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Buckeyes' Campbell makes moves for impressive run
videos.description: Parris Campbell zig-zags down field for a 44-yard run, putting Ohio State in scoring position.

videos.headline: Ohio State's Barrett runs in for TD
videos.description: J.T. Barrett  runs for 3 yards and stretches his arm out for a Buckeyes' touchdown.

videos.headline: Buckeyes' Weber with 43-yard TD
videos.description: Mike Weber sprints down the sidelines for an Ohio State touchdown.

videos.headline: Barrett throws 100th TD pass of career
videos.description: J.T. Barrett finds Binjimen Victor for an 11-yard touchdown, becoming the first Ohio State QB to reach 100 career touchdown passes.

videos.headline: Buckeyes' Weber carries defenders for first down
videos.description: Ohio State's Mike Weber runs up the middle for 22 yards, carrying multiple defenders for a first down.

videos.headline: Ohio State's Dobbins pushes through for TD
videos.description: J.K. Dobbins takes the hand off and runs it up the middle, pushing through defenders for a Buckeyes' touchdown.

videos.headline: Ohio State fumble leads to Illinois TD
videos.description: Buckeyes' Dwayne Haskins fumbles the ball and is recovered by Fighting Illini's Ahmari Hayes and takes it to the house 54 yards.

videos.headline: Illinois turns it over on punt return
videos.description: Fighting Illini's Nate Hobbs fumbles on the punt return, which leads to the Buckeyes' Jeffrey Okudah recovering the ball.

videos.headline: Buckeyes extend lead with Baugh TD
videos.description: J.T. Barrett finds Marcus Baugh wide open for a 12-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Illinois' Crouch sacked late in the third
videos.description: Chayce Crouch gets sacked by Ohio State's Jonathan Cooper, for Cooper's first sack of the season.

videos.headline: Buckeyes extend lead with Victor's TD catch
videos.description: Ohio State's Dwayne Haskins' pass is complete to Binjimen Victor for a 21-yard touchdown catch.

videos.headline: Illinois' Brown with 30-yard run
videos.description: Fighting Illini's Dre Brown jukes out Buckeyes and runs for 30 yards for a first down.

videos.headline: Illinois' backup QB runs in TD
videos.description: Fighting Illini's backup quarterback Cam Miller, runs in a 9-yard touchdown on his first snap of the game.
